Note on bundled artefacts:

The MagicBathyNet *dataset* (Agrafiotis et al. 2024) is **not** redistributed
in this repository. Two tiny sample tiles included under data/sample/ are
shown only for demo purposes and remain under the dataset's original
CC-BY-NC-SA 4.0 license; please cite the dataset paper if you use them.

Pre-trained model weights distributed via Git LFS are released under the
same MIT license as the code; cite the PhysSDB paper if you reuse them in
your own work.
